high_descs: Turn to the left and walk straight to face the black kitchen table.
Pick the spoon up from off of the table.
Turn around, go straight then turn left to face the stove.
Place the spoon in the pan on the right rear burner.
Pick the pan on the right rear burner up.
Turn to the left, go straight then go to the left to face the side of the black kitchen table.
Place the pan on the black kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan with the spoon in it on the black kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the black circle table.
Pick up the spoon on the table.
Turn around and walk towards the stove to your left.
Place the spoon in the pan closest to you on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the spoon.
Turn left and walk back towards the black circle table.
Place the pan with the spoon near the white cup on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan with the spoon near on the circle table.

high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the round black table.
Pick up the closest metal spoon off of the round table.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the stove.
Put the spoon in the frying pan that is on the front right burner of the stove.
Pick up the frying pan with the metal spoon in it off of the stove.
Turn left and walk over to the round black table.
Put the frying pan with the metal spoon in it on the round black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spoon in it on the table.
